name: ./doc/manual/installation.md
content:
# Installation
Can be managed using
[jspm](http://jspm.io)
or [npm](https://github.com/npm/npm).

### jspm
```terminal
jspm install npm:@aureooms/js-measure
```

### npm
```terminal
npm install @aureooms/js-measure --save
```
